note.body:
Marking as Draft again, because the branch is based on https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/NetworkManager-libreswan/-/merge_requests/38 and the first three commits come from there:

```
dbdb12b shared: make ipsec.conf formatting declarative
4ecdda9 service: drop nm_ls_*_validate()
24e493f shared: make ipsec.conf parsing declarative
```

The rest is part of this branch:

```
8b61ebe all: rename som defines to fit with the pattern
86b92b3 shared/utils: add routines to parse and normalize subnet lists
fdf07a3 editor: fix indentation
7439559 editor: do not allow funny characters while editing
4db1fb0 editor: validate some fields in advanced dialog
26e2990 NEWS: add a mention about the validation
97f967e all: add support for leftsubnets/rightsubnets
6ddf41d NEWS: document addittion of leftsubnets/rightsubnets
```
